      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, a high-revving powerplant with an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal rear-axle traction. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring internal tolerances are within factory specifications. The chassis remains composed with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear geometry providing excellent lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical synchronization and induction note remain superlative.",
